It should not remove the "if" from "else if" tags
{% if condition1 %}
  Condition1 is truthy
{% else if condition2 %}
  Condition2 is truthy
{% endif %}

It should format elseif tags
{% if condition1 %}
  Condition1 is truthy
{% elseif condition2 %}
  Condition2 is truthy
{% else %}
  Something else
{% endif %}
